        <header>
            <h1><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Iris Flower Classification</h1>
            <p class="description">Enter the measurements of an iris flower to classify its species and visualize the data</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="left-panel">
                <div class="input-section">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> Enter Flower Measurements</h2>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <label for="sepal-length">Sepal Length (cm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="sepal-length" step="0.1" min="4.0" max="8.0" placeholder="e.g., 5.4">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <label for="sepal-width">Sepal Width (cm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="sepal-width" step="0.1" min="2.0" max="4.5" placeholder="e.g., 3.2">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <label for="petal-length">Petal Length (cm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="petal-length" step="0.1" min="1.0" max="7.0" placeholder="e.g., 4.5">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <label for="petal-width">Petal Width (cm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="petal-width" step="0.1" min="0.1" max="2.5" placeholder="e.g., 1.5">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button id="classify-btn"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Classify Flower</button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="chart-container">
                    <div class="chart-title">Measurement Visualization</div>
                    <canvas id="measurementChart"></canvas>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-section">
                    <h2 class="info-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Iris Flowers</h2>
                    <div class="info-content">
                        <p>The Iris flower data set is a classic dataset in pattern recognition and machine learning. It contains three classes of 50 instances each, where each class refers to a type of iris plant.</p>
                        <p>This tool uses a machine learning model to classify iris flowers based on four features: sepal length, sepal width, petal length, and petal width.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
